OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772885580
OL,3,CCost of heating oil increases by over
OL,4,C80% in seven days for NI customers
OL,6,FThere have been calls for transparency
OL,7,Fover why the cost of home heating oil
OL,8,Fhas increased so dramatically over the
OL,9,Flast week.
OL,11,FWhile the conflict in the Middle East
OL,12,Fhas pushed up the price of a barrel of
OL,13,Foil by around 20%, the latest figures
OL,14,Fon Thursday show the cost to customers
OL,15,Fin Northern Ireland has shot up by
OL,16,Fmore than 80%.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772885580
OL,3,CCost of heating oil increases by over
OL,4,C80% in seven days for NI customers
OL,6,FFlights are beginning to take out of
OL,7,Fthe Middle East, bringing stranded
OL,8,Fholiday makers to the UK and Ireland,
OL,9,Fwhile missile and drone attacks in the
OL,10,Fregion continue.
OL,12,FThe Economy Minister held a meeting on
OL,13,FThursday afternoon amid concerns about
OL,14,Fthe rising prices.
OL,16,FCaoimhe Archibald MLA said: "The point
OL,17,Fthat I wanted to get across is that we
OL,18,Fneed to have transparency around why
OL,19,Fwe have seen such significant price
OL,20,Frises over the past number of days.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772885580
OL,3,CCost of heating oil increases by over
OL,4,C80% in seven days for NI customers
OL,6,F"People have to understand what has
OL,7,Fcaused this and to be very clear that
OL,8,Fthere have not been unjustified price
OL,9,Fhikes, if that is the case."
OL,11,FThe figures themselves are stark.
OL,13,FLast week, the Consumer Council said
OL,14,Fthe average price of 500 litres of oil
OL,15,Fwas #307.
OL,17,FIn the latest figures announced on
OL,18,FThursday, the cost was more than #550.
OL,19,FThat's an 81% increase in seven days.
OL,21,FThere are ongoing strikes in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
