OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772885580
OL,3,CCost of heating oil increases by over
OL,4,C80% in seven days for NI customers
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister spent Thursday
OL,7,Fafternoon justifying his position over
OL,8,Frecent days.
OL,10,FKeir Starmer is all too aware of the
OL,11,Fknock-on effect the war is having on
OL,12,Fpeople and the economy.
OL,14,FThe Prime Minister said: "We will lay
OL,15,Fon additional charter flights in the
OL,16,Fcoming days. British Airways is
OL,17,Fputting on daily flights from Oman,
OL,18,Fand we will keep working with all of
OL,19,Four partners to increase the speed and
OL,20,Fcapacity of this airlift.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772885580
OL,3,CCost of heating oil increases by over
OL,4,C80% in seven days for NI customers
OL,6,F"Iran is targeting oil and gas
OL,7,Ffacilities in the Gulf and tankers in
OL,8,Fthe Straits of Hormuz, trying to
OL,9,Finflict economic pain around the
OL,10,Fworld. So we will continue to work
OL,11,Fwith the industries affected and our
OL,12,Fallies to respond to any impact."
OL,14,FThere's no end in sight to this
OL,15,Fconflict, and while the UK isn't
OL,16,Fdirectly involved, the effect it's
OL,17,Fhaving on money in our pockets is
OL,18,Falready being felt.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
